{"type":null,"faqId":19395,"title":"如何升级手机？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n.s4{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;color:blue;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=64277\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>为防止手机内存中的用户数据（如：联系人、信息、通话记录等）在升级时被删除，建议升级前备份手机数据。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>在线升级（HOTA升级）：在线升级前，请连接移动网络或 </span><span class=\"s2\">WLAN</span><span> 网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>在主屏幕，点击</span><span class=\"s3\">系统软件更新</span><span>&gt;</span><span class=\"s3\">在线升级</span><span>，根据屏幕提示完成升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>本地升级：进入华为终端官网 </span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s4\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</span></a><span> 下载软件升级包，并将 </span><span class=\"s2\">dload</span><span> 文件夹放入手机内部存储根目录下。插入 </span><span class=\"s2\">microSD</span><span> 卡，并将升级包中的 </span><span class=\"s2\">dload</span><span> 文件夹放入 </span><span class=\"s2\">microSD</span><span> 卡根目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>在主屏幕，点击</span><span class=\"s3\">系统软件更新</span><span>&gt;</span><span class=\"s3\">本地升级</span><span>，根据屏幕提示完成升级。您也可以参考下载的软件升级包中的升级指导。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":141,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2536","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608227000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":265,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}